{"tid":412841,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴舒亞伊嫌能力值80太低 FIFA開發商EA：開個99比你","createTime":"2017-09-25T04:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T13:45:10.000Z","uid":31314,"like":83,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1fc70ab8bb42e85cdf803d7ecd46f58f6a5c3c07","tid":412841,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"近日《FIFA18》開發商EA公佈了遊戲內各球員的能力值，然而車路士前鋒巴舒亞伊（Batshuayi）能力值為80，球員本人對此略有意見並向EA反映，竟獲官方「認真」回應。<br />\n<br />\n當巴舒亞伊得知自己遊戲內能力值為80時，變得一臉疑惑並不滿，更即時透過社交網站Twitter向EA官方反映，當時EA的回復是：「繼續進球吧，然後我們再談。」巴舒亞伊亦笑稱：「有道理，但我已經長時間都能穩定入球，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>甚至比你們的伺服器還要穩定。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而在昨日聯賽盃的賽事中，巴舒亞伊個人連中三元完成「帽子戲法」，賽後隨即於Twitter向EA詢問：「現在可以討論了嗎？」然後EA官方竟發出一張巴舒亞伊能力值為99的圖片，巴舒亞伊即時回應：「這能力值對現在的我太高了，留給以後吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2017/09/20170922_FIFA18_5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2017%2F09%2F20170922_FIFA18_5.jpg&h=1518b687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這場遊戲商與球員的「罵戰」相當「搞笑」，不少網民都留意支持巴舒亞伊，希望將來佢真的配得上99的能力值。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2017/09/20170922_FIFA18_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2017%2F09%2F20170922_FIFA18_1.jpg&h=9152b87d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"488982b982b4aad46c861412976ba954a524c672","tid":412841,"uid":4525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"煩膠"},{"pid":"d0095fe439f72404ab77971250fbcb5d5dabdcfc","tid":412841,"uid":33601,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:14:16.000Z","msg":"80都比多佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fbfaa7492a93a5e76c89bdb3315747ee4160ba","tid":412841,"uid":12980,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:16:09.000Z","msg":"電腦分析"},{"p